(115,68,3,'Exbom BK-S1000 wireless keyboard','Exbom BK-S1000 slim wireless keyboard (ABNT2).','Budget 2.4 GHz keyboard + mouse kit for Brazil layout.','AAA powered, ~10 m range.','2026-03-29 12:00:00','2026-03-29 12:00:00'),
(116,69,3,'Intelbras IPR 800 conference phone','Intelbras IPR 800 analog conference phone.','Tabletop speakerphone for small meeting rooms.','Omni mic, mute, LCD, PSTN analog.','2026-03-29 12:00:00','2026-03-29 12:00:00'),
